(319,'Triceps, Shoulders and Chest Boost','Workout','Overhead Tricep extention',45,'Weights or Bands','http://static.giantbomb.com/uploads/scale_small/13/135472/1891763-006charizard.png','Stand or Sit on a low-back seat holding a relatively light dumbbell in each hand. Begin with the dumbbells overhead and your arms fully extended toward the ceiling. Bend your arms to lower the dumbbells behind your head. When your elbows reach just past 90 degrees, extend them to return to the start position'),
